Assign Einstein Discovery Permission Sets to Users

You are here: SALESFORCE HELP > DOCS > ANALYTICS

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS
To assign a permission set to users:

From Setup, enter Permission Sets and select Permission Sets.
Click the permission set you want to assign to users. Assign the Manage Einstein Discovery permission set only to users who administer Einstein Discovery.
Click Manage Assignments, and click Add Assignments.
Select one or more users, and click Assign.
Click Done.
